      • DownsamplingSpecification

        public DownsamplingSpecification(long interval,
                                 Aggregator function,
                                 FillPolicy fill_policy)
        已过时。 since 2.3
        Non-stringified, piecewise c-tor.
        参数:
        interval - The downsampling interval, in milliseconds.
        function - The downsampling function.
        fill_policy - The policy specifying how to deal with missing data.
        抛出:
        IllegalArgumentException - if any argument is invalid.

      • DownsamplingSpecification

        public DownsamplingSpecification(String specification)
        C-tor for string representations. The argument to this c-tor should have the following format: interval-function[-fill_policy]. This ctor supports the "all" flag to downsample to a single value as well as units suffixed with 'c' to use the calendar for downsample alignment.
        参数:
        specification - String representation of a downsample specifier.
        抛出:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the specification is null or invalid.
